Per discussion in the yarn-dev@, http://mail-archives.apache.org/mod_mbox/hadoop-yarn-dev/201305.mbox/browser , as per Bobby suggestion, a simple way to do this would be something along the following lines:

{code}
public interface RecordFactory {
  public <T> T newRecordInstance(Class<T> clazz) throws YarnException;

public <T> T newRecordInstance(Class<T> clazz, byte[] data) throws
YarnException;

public <T> byte[] fromRecordInstance(T t) throws YarnException;
}
{code}

